message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which is valued at $12,000 by both myself and you. Considering its exceptional quality and value, I am offering it to you today at an exclusive price of $11,000. This is a special opportunity to own a product that I believe will significantly enhance your experience and meet your needs better than any alternative on the market. I look forward to hearing your decision soon. Thank you for considering this offer.
